    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Cone, Cylinder, Plane

    public class Orientable
extends GeometricPrimitive
implements SITBase
    The ontological descriptor of an orientable object.

    This class describes extends the basic GeometricPrimitive by considering also a direction of the principal axis, in accord with the ontological structure.
